-detroit/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3730226-143908021866dd9eeab725428196c2a7f402e35745.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/motor-city-hop-the-top-five-bars-in-detroit/"><h3>Motor City Hop | The Top 5 Bars In Detroit</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">We highlight the top five bars in Detroit for a local nightlife experience. </div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1437629983"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-best-markets-in-detroit/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3711374-eastern.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-best-markets-in-detroit/"><h3>The Best Markets in Detroit</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Check out these weekday &amp; weekend markets happening in the Detroit area. </div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1437324062"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-top-10-things-to-do-and-see-in-detroit-s-east-side/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3699837-1436241452bfefa4db18c94bccbb1d7d57632d1583.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-top-10-things-to-do-and-see-in-detroit-s-east-side/"><h3>The Top 10 Things To Do and See in Detroit’s East Side</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Historical sites, parks, and a century-old ceramic studio - here are the best things to do in Detroit's East Side.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1428332674"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-10-most-beautiful-towns-in-michigan/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3637718-14279125355282073e2b2642798a830de86856173c.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/the-10-most-beautiful-towns-in-michigan/"><h3>The 10 Most Beautiful Towns in Michigan</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Check out our guide to some of Michigan’s most beautiful towns and discover the charming, must-visit towns in the state.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1425935185"><a href="/north-america/usa/articles/the-10-best-beer-towns-in-america/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3631427-142585635051146436ede3456a9f0577e5a78e940c.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/articles/the-10-best-beer-towns-in-america/"><h3>The 10 Best Beer Towns in America</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">We take a look at the towns that are driving the USA's craft beer revolution - where does yours stack up?</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1416487896"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/frozen-lighthouse-will-leave-you-with-chills/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-290479-tom-gill5.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/frozen-lighthouse-will-leave-you-with-chills/"><h3>Frozen Lighthouse Will Leave You with Chills</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Stunning photos of lighthouse on Lake Michigan after an extreme winter.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1409586922"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/detroit-s-top-10-restaurants-you-should-try-motown-dining/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-279954-56-274481-header-image.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/detroit-s-top-10-restaurants-you-should-try-motown-dining/"><h3>Detroit’s Top 10 Restaurants You Should Try | Motown Dining</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Experience Motor Town’s dining scene with our culture lover’s guide to the 10 best restaurants, eateries and barbeque joints in Detroit, Michigan.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>Michigan Music</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li></ul><div class="panel-content"><a href="#" class="left presentation-nav"></a><a href="#" class="right presentation-nav"></a><div class="presentation-container"><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1437632124"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/detroit-five-iconic-albums-that-have-made-music-history/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3699732-1436228848ff47545e238844c79293b96b2dff50fa.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/detroit-five-iconic-albums-that-have-made-music-history/"><h3>Detroit: Five Iconic Albums That Have Made Music History</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Discover some of the historic and infamous albums that stem from Detroit. </div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1387387009"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/from-motown-to-8-mile-the-music-of-detroit-michigan/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-279956-56-230530-detroitskyline.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/usa/michigan/articles/from-motown-to-8-mile-the-music-of-detroit-michigan/"><h3>From Motown to 8 Mile: The Music of Detroit, Michigan</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Between Lake Erie and Lake St. Clair in America's Midwest, Detroit, Michigan has become America's Comeback City, retaining its musical identity against all odds.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel profile"><h2>Michigan Profile</h2><div class="panel-overflow"><div class="panel-content"><img src="http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/19-19970-685px-flag-of-michigan.png" alt="Michigan Flag" class="float-image-left" height="84" width="140"/><div class="text"><p>Michigan is made up of two peninsulas which fit into the Great Lakes,
the name Michigan unsurprisingly comes from a distortion of the Ojibwa name
meaning ‘large water’.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Cited when Toni
Morrison was awarded the Nobel Prize for literature in 1993, <em>Song of Solomon </em>is about an African-American who lives in Michigan. A very different book, also set in Michigan,
is Elmore Leonard’s <em>Swag</em>. </p>
<p> </p>
<p>Multi-award winning teen-comedy <em>American Pie</em> presents a well-worn image of what high school
graduation is considered. <em>Anatomy of Murder</em>
gives a very different image of Michigan, which is a courtroom trial drama.
</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Michigan offers a diverse music scene, mainly focused around
the main city of Detroit, ranging from Eminem,
The White Stripes and The Stooges<strong>, </strong>as
well as being home to the Detroit
Symphony Orchestra. </p></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><a href="" class="expand">Expand</a></div></div>
			
